                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170219-156-victim1157 t18170219-156-viclabel889"></join>. The prisoner was my <rs id="t18170219-156-deflabel890" type="occupation">apprentice</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170219-156-defend1156 t18170219-156-deflabel890"></join>. On the 8th of February, I sent him to Mr. Harris to sell some hands, he brought me back ten shillings, and said, that was all he could get for them. He has lived ten years with me. When he was detected, he said, he had lost three shillings.</p>
